        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "## What's needed\n\nThe NIST SRD-46 (Critically Selected Stability Constants of Metal Complexes) database stores stability constants **per specific metal–ligand system**. To search effectively, I need you to specify:\n\n1. **Metal ion** (and oxidation state) — e.g., Cu²⁺, Fe³⁺, Zn²⁺\n2. **Ligand** — e.g., EDTA, glycine, oxalate, chloride",
